text.section:
An insurer issuing a group or individual health benefit plan may offer a voluntary wellness or health improvement program that allows for rewards or incentives to encourage participation or to reward members for participation, including but not limited to:
Merchandise;
Gift cards;
Debit cards;
Premium discounts or rebates;
Contributions toward a member's health savings account;
Modification to copayment, deductible, or coinsurance amounts; or
Any combination of the incentives authorized by paragraphs (a) to (f) of this subsection.
